{"tid":610014,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"不得不說 能夠欣賞廢萌動漫係做人嘅最高境界","createTime":"2018-03-29T13:54:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T14:13:11.000Z","uid":59491,"like":10,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"79670bc0a34c9f4aaed4b0e529b9c49909786f7b","tid":610014,"uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T13:54:07.000Z","msg":"細蚊仔個陣 覺得廢萌冇嘢睇 唔知佢地係度鳩下鳩下咁做乜鳩 睇下熱血打鬥仲爽<br />\n<br />\n中學大學個陣 就為咗認識自我 了解宇宙起源同人生意義 而睇深度番 <br />\n同時又因為覺得睇深度番好高品味 睇唔起廢萌番<br />\n<br />\n出黎做嘢個陣 發覺呢啲先係好嘢黎 見到佢地鳩下鳩下咁 <br />\n但相比自己做到隻狗咁 反而想追求呢種鳩下鳩下愉快過每一日嘅生活<br />\n廢萌治癒人心呀!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.cocohk.today/upload/tU/1fB/8535ccb755a14b81aac99e0a45e88199.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cocohk.today%2Fupload%2FtU%2F1fB%2F8535ccb755a14b81aac99e0a45e88199.jpg&h=a1874db5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">[black]FF下好啦 過完個復活節準時返工啦[/black]</span>"},{"pid":"a2a3bf5ab1608c73139fcd24ca20f02ddbbf234b","tid":610014,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T13:57:55.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"52c3716bbc803d9ff902520ac4b82347c46a570c","tid":610014,"uid":41524,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T14:02:24.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪返工俾人排既毒男?"},{"pid":"86d08791e754bd4df5659fa9095470d9be53ba59","tid":610014,"uid":34622,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T14:03:25.000Z","msg":"new game 係撚廢萌呀樓主，你就廢鳩死毒撚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"054a4c11068d5ed64c4783ec0217bcb05a7f1a24","tid":610014,"uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52c3716bbc803d9ff902520ac4b82347c46a570c","tid":610014,"uid":41524,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T14